name: Impostor Syndrome (itch) (MidnightLaboratory)
description:
Your friend has gotten hold of the only key to a mysterious property in the middle of the desert. He's called you up for a night ride to check the place out. What could possibly wrong?

Venture out into the Bahraini desert and discover a mysterious facility...


What could be behind this door?


What could these contraptions do?

...Only one way to find out!
